headline: Stifel Reaffirms Buy Rating on ONEOK, Inc. (OKE)
summary: ONEOK, Inc. (NYSE:OKE) is one of the 13 best oil and gas storage stocks to buy according to hedge funds. On February 24, Stifel Nicolaus reiterated its Buy rating on ONEOK, Inc. (NYSE:OKE).
